description: Try our easy to follow Vegetarian Sausage Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Vegetarian Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 sheet frozen readyrolled 25% reduced fat puff pastry
1.5 cup creamed cottage cheese (97% fat free)

recipeInstructions.text: Brush sausage rolls with the egg wash and sprinkle with poppy seeds. Bake for 25 minutes or until sausage rolls are golden and cooked through. Serve.
